---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="管理后台" description="博客内容管理系统">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto py-8">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8">博客管理后台</h1>

    <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 mb-8">
      <a
        href="/dashboard/"
        class="p-6 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-50 to-primary-100 dark:from-primary-900/30 dark:to-primary-800/30 rounded-xl hover:shadow-lg transition-all hover:scale-[1.02]"
      >
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-primary-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M11 5H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v11a2 2 0 002 2h11a2 2 0 002-2v-5m-1.414-9.414a2 2 0 112.828 2.828L11.828 15H9v-2.828l8.586-8.586z" />
          </svg>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold">内容编辑</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">创建和编辑文章、页面</p>
      </a>

      <a
        href="/admin/"
        class="p-6 bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 rounded-xl hover:border-primary-500 hover:shadow-lg transition-all hover:scale-[1.02]"
      >
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-primary-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 11H5m14 0a2 2 0 012 2v6a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-6a2 2 0 012-2m14 0V9a2 2 0 00-2-2M5 11V9a2 2 0 012-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h6a2 2 0 012 2v2M7 7h10" />
          </svg>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold">Decap CMS</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">可视化编辑器（需配置）</p>
      </a>

      <a
        href="/"
        class="p-6 bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 rounded-xl hover:border-primary-500 hover:shadow-lg transition-all hover:scale-[1.02]"
      >
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-primary-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" />
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M2.458 12C3.732 7.943 7.523 5 12 5c4.478 0 8.268 2.943 9.542 7-1.274 4.057-5.064 7-9.542 7-4.477 0-8.268-2.943-9.542-7z" />
          </svg>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold">预览博客</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">查看博客首页</p>
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 p-6 mb-6">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">快速操作</h2>
      <div class="grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4">
        <a
          href="/dashboard/"
          class="flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-3 bg-primary-600 text-white rounded-lg hover:bg-primary-700 transition-colors"
        >
          <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 4v16m8-8H4" />
          </svg>
          开始写作
        </a>
        <a
          href="/search/"
          class="flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-3 bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-700 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-200 dark:hover:bg-gray-600 transition-colors"
        >
          <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 21l-6-6m2-5a7 7 0 11-14 0 7 7 0 0114 0z" />
          </svg>
          搜索内容
        </a>
        <a
          href="/archives/"
          class="flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-3 bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-700 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-200 dark:hover:bg-gray-600 transition-colors"
        >
          <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 7V3m8 4V3m-9 8h10M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z" />
          </svg>
          文章归档
        </a>
        <a
          href="/rss.xml"
          target="_blank"
          class="flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-3 bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-700 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-200 dark:hover:bg-gray-600 transition-colors"
        >
          <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 5c7.18 0 13 5.82 13 13M6 11a7 7 0 017 7" />
          </svg>
          RSS 订阅
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">
      <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 p-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">使用说明</h2>
        <ol class="list-decimal list-inside space-y-3 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
          <li>点击"开始写作"进入配置页面</li>
          <li>按照说明配置 GitHub 仓库信息</li>
          <li>部署后使用 GitHub OAuth 登录 CMS</li>
          <li>创建或编辑文章内容</li>
          <li>保存后自动提交到 GitHub</li>
          <li>合并后网站自动更新</li>
        </ol>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 p-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">文章格式</h2>
        <pre class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-900 p-4 rounded-lg text-sm overflow-x-auto"><code>---
title: 文章标题
date: 2026-04-24
category: 技术
tags: [标签1, 标签2]
excerpt: 文章摘要
draft: false
pinned: false
---

文章内容使用 Markdown 格式...</code></pre>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-8 p-6 bg-primary-50 dark:bg-primary-900/20 rounded-xl">
      <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2 flex items-center gap-2">
        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
        </svg>
        提示
      </h3>
      <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 text-sm">
        Decap CMS 支持完整的可视化编辑，包括 Markdown 编辑器、拖拽上传图片、实时预览等功能。
        配置完成后，你可以通过任何浏览器在线管理博客内容，无需安装任何软件。
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
